@startuml SD_11_VoucherValidation
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Tạo & Áp dụng Voucher
' FR-33~FR-36: Create Voucher + Validate at Checkout
' ============================================================

title **SD-11: Tạo & Áp dụng Voucher\n(Create + Validate + Apply)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
    ParticipantBorderColor #F9A825
    ArrowColor #F9A825
}

actor "Organizer" as Organizer #Gold
participant "Organizer\nBrowser" as OrgBrowser #LightYellow
participant "VoucherServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #FFFDE7
participant "VoucherService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "VoucherDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

actor "Attendee" as Customer #LightBlue
participant "Customer\nBrowser" as CustBrowser #LightYellow
participant "CheckoutServlet" as ChkCtrl #FCE4EC

== Part A: Organizer Tạo Event Voucher ==

Organizer -> OrgBrowser: Truy cập Quản lý Voucher
OrgBrowser -> Controller: GET /organizer/vouchers/create\n?eventId={id}
activate Controller
Controller --> OrgBrowser: Forward → create-voucher.jsp
deactivate Controller
OrgBrowser --> Organizer: Form tạo voucher

Organizer -> OrgBrowser: Nhập thông tin voucher
OrgBrowser -> Controller: POST /organizer/vouchers/create\n{code: "SUMMER2025",\ndiscountType: "percentage",\ndiscountValue: 20,\nminOrderAmount: 200000,\nmaxDiscount: 100000,\nusageLimit: 50,\nstartDate, endDate,\neventId, scope: "EVENT"}
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: Validate:\n- code unique\n- discountValue > 0\n- startDate < endDate\n- usageLimit > 0

Controller -> Service: createVoucher(voucherData)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: findByCode("SUMMER2025")
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Vouchers\nWHERE code = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: null (unique)
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: null
deactivate DAO

Service -> DAO: create(voucher)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO Vouchers\n(voucherId, code, discountType,\ndiscountValue, minOrderAmount,\nmaxDiscount, usageLimit,\nusedCount=0, startDate, endDate,\neventId, scope='EVENT',\nfundSource='ORGANIZER',\nisActive=true, createdAt)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Created
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: Voucher
deactivate DAO

Service --> Controller: Voucher created
deactivate Service
Controller --> OrgBrowser: Redirect + flash:\n"Voucher SUMMER2025 đã tạo"
deactivate Controller
OrgBrowser --> Organizer: ✅ Voucher đã tạo

== Part B: Attendee Áp dụng Voucher (Checkout) ==

Customer -> CustBrowser: Tại trang Checkout,\nnhập mã "SUMMER2025"
CustBrowser -> ChkCtrl: POST /checkout/validate-voucher\n{voucherCode: "SUMMER2025",\ntotalAmount: 500000,\neventId: 123}
activate ChkCtrl

ChkCtrl -> Service: validateAndCalculate(\n"SUMMER2025", 500000, eventId=123)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: findByCode("SUMMER2025")
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Vouchers\nWHERE code = 'SUMMER2025'
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Voucher
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: Voucher
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: **Validation Chain (7 bước):**

note right of Service
  1. ✅ Voucher exists
  2. ✅ isActive == true
  3. ✅ now ≥ startDate
  4. ✅ now ≤ endDate
  5. ✅ usedCount(15) < usageLimit(50)
  6. ✅ totalAmount(500K) ≥ minOrderAmount(200K)
  7. ✅ scope check:
     voucher.eventId == order.eventId
end note

Service -> Service: **Calculate Discount:**\nType = percentage (20%)\nRaw = 500000 × 20% = 100,000\nCapped = min(100000, maxDiscount=100000)\n→ **discountAmount = 100,000₫**

Service -> Service: **Split Fund Source:**\nvoucher.fundSource = 'ORGANIZER'\n→ eventDiscountAmount = 100,000\n→ systemDiscountAmount = 0

Service --> ChkCtrl: VoucherResult {\n  valid: true,\n  discountAmount: 100000,\n  eventDiscount: 100000,\n  systemDiscount: 0,\n  finalTotal: 400000\n}
deactivate Service

ChkCtrl --> CustBrowser: JSON {\n  success: true,\n  discount: "100,000₫",\n  newTotal: "400,000₫",\n  message: "Giảm 20% (tối đa 100K)"\n}
deactivate ChkCtrl

CustBrowser -> CustBrowser: Update UI:\nDiscount: -100,000₫\nTổng thanh toán: 400,000₫
CustBrowser --> Customer: ✅ Voucher áp dụng thành công

@enduml
